Days of Our Lives actor Freddie Smith was injured and his girlfriend was airlifted to a hospital in critical condition after his car lost control on bend.

The crash involving Smith and girlfriend Alyssa Tabit occurred Tuesday near Ashtabula, roughly 55 miles northeast of Cleveland.

Emergency responders found Tabit of North Hollywood, California, trapped in the car.  

